Leslie Banning https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leslie_Banning 0 Leslie Banning (born Mary Louise Welch) is a retired American film actress. She is sometimes credited as Leslye Banning. Banning attended Glendale High School.Banning signed a contract with Universal International in 1949. She played the female lead in the Western film Cactus Caravan (1951).On May 1, 1949, Banning married Wallace Russell, brother of actress Jane Russell. In 1974, her married name was Mary Lou Rogers; she was married to a teacher in Simi Valley, California. Leslie_Banning ( born Mary_Louise Welch ) is a_retired_American_film_actress .
